<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ARES - Official Website</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #926F34;
      --secondary-color: rgba(0, 0, 0);
      --text-color: #FFFFFF;
      --overlay-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      --tertiary-color: #202024;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--secondary-color);
      color: var(--text-color);
    }

    header {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 80px;
      background-color: var(--secondary-color);
      padding: 10px 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    header .logo {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }

    header nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    header nav a {
      color: var(--text-color);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    header nav a:hover {
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 50px;
      background-color: var(--secondary-color);
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 0;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    footer a {
      color: var(--primary-color);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      color: #71592a;
    }

    .background-slideshow {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .background-image {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1s;
    }

    .background-image.visible {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      background-color: var(--overlay-color);
      padding: 20px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .game-title {
      font-size: 100px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 180px;
      margin-bottom: 100px;
      color: var(--text-color);
    }

    .cta-group {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      width: 300px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .cta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      background-color: var(--secondary-color);
      color: var(--text-color);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 400;
      border: 1px solid var(--primary-color);
    }

    .cta:hover {
      background-color: var(--primary-color);
      color: var(--secondary-color);
      border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);
    }

    .cta img {
      margin-right: 10px;
      height: 20px;
    }

    .game-description {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      width: 600px;
    }

    .info-section {
      background-color: #0f1116;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      width: 300px;
      margin: 20px auto;
    }

    .info-value {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .info-value img {
      height: 20px;
    }

    .info-item {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #333333;
    }

    .info-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .info-label {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #777;
    }

    .features {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 50px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .features .feature {
      flex: 1;
      max-width: 300px;
      background: var(--tertiary-color);
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    .features .feature:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }

    .features .feature h3 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .features .feature p {
      color: #E5E5E5;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
      .features {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="logo">ARES</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="#features">Features</a>
      <a href="#info">Info</a>
      <a href="#downloads">Download</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <div class="background-slideshow">
    <img class="background-image" src="images/ares_screenshot1.png" alt="Background 1">
    <img class="background-image" src="images/ares_screenshot2.png" alt="Background 2">
    <img class="background-image" src="images/ares_screenshot3.png" alt="Background 3">
    <img class="background-image" src="images/ares_screenshot4.png" alt="Background 4">
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h1 class="game-title">ARES</h1>

    <div class="cta-group">
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=macOS-file-id" class="cta">
        <img src="images/apple_logo.png" alt="Apple Logo"> Download for MacOS
      </a>
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=windows-file-id" class="cta">
        <img src="images/win11_logo.png" alt="Windows Logo"> Download for Windows
      </a>
      <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/" class="cta">
        <img src="images/steam_logo.png" alt="Steam Logo"> Get it on Steam
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="game-description">
      <p>
        Step into the world of <strong>ARES</strong>, the ultimate <strong>multiplayer</strong> experience! Challenge your friends or team up with them in epic battles featuring thrilling game modes like <strong>Deathmatch</strong>, <strong>Domain</strong>, and <strong>Survival</strong>. Explore breathtaking <strong>realistic graphics</strong> and immerse yourself in an action-packed journey. Customize your <strong>weapons</strong> to match your unique playstyle and get ready to dominate the battlefield. The fun begins now!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-section">
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">Developer</span>
        <span class="info-value">Cristiano Rotunno</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">Distributor</span>
        <span class="info-value">ARES Studio</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">Release Date</span>
        <span class="info-value">2025</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">Platforms</span>
        <span class="info-value">
          <img src="images/win11_logo.png" alt="Windows">
          <img src="images/apple_logo.png" alt="MacOS">
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Realistic Graphics</h3>
        <p>Immerse yourself in a world with next-generation graphic details.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Dynamic Multiplayer</h3>
        <p>Take on epic challenges in advanced multiplayer mode.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Total Customization</h3>
        <p>Create your own unique style with customizable gear.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>Â© 2025 ARES. All rights reserved. <a href="#privacy">Privacy Policy</a></p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    const images = document.querySelectorAll('.background-image');
    let currentIndex = 0;

    function changeBackground() {
      images[currentIndex].classList.remove('visible');
      currentIndex = (currentIndex + 1) % images.length;
      images[currentIndex].classList.add('visible');
    }

    setInterval(changeBackground, 5000);
  </script>
</body>
</html>
